p: In obedience to the within writ I herewith bring into court the body of the within named George W Kirk alias G W Kerr & who was committed to my custody by Justice Herkenrath a Justice of the Peace for St Louis County in the 14th day of June 1856 which is heretinto appended and made a part of this return St Louis Aug 11 1856
Habeas Corpus in matter of George W Kirk
